Package: representr
Type: Package
Title: Create Representative Records Post-Record Linkage
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("XXXX", "XXXX", email = "XXXX.XXXX@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates representative records for use in downstream tasks after 
    record linkage is performed. Multiple methods for creating the records are 
    provided, including two methods based on the posterior distribution of linkage
    resulting from a Bayesian analysis.
